#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.klevernotes.metainfo.xml:33
msgid ""
"KleverNotes is a note taking and management application for your mobile and "
"desktop devices. It uses markdown and allow you to preview your content."
msgstr ""
"KleverNotes je aplikacija za vnos opomb in upravljanje za vaše mobilne in "
"namizne naprave. Uporablja markdown in dovoljuje predogled vaše vsebine."

